In terms of applications, coconut milk powder finds extensive usage in the food and beverage industry, where it is utilized in a wide range of products such as curries, desserts, beverages, and baked goods. The versatility of coconut milk powder as a dairy alternative and flavor enhancer has contributed to its popularity among food manufacturers and consumers seeking plant-based options. Additionally, the use of coconut milk powder in cosmetics and pharmaceuticals is witnessing growth, driven by the natural and nourishing properties of coconut-derived ingredients.

